        <body>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Clerk's Office U S. Cir Court</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>St Paul</placeName>
                <date>Oct 30. 1862</date>.</p>
            <p><addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">At a meeting of the<lb/> Israelites of this city (few in number)
                freed<lb/> last <date>Sunday</date>, it was proposed and<lb/> agreed to open a
                Jewish Sunday School<lb/> in this City under the instruction of a<lb/>
                <persName>Mr <hi rend="underline">Marcuson</hi></persName>, with whom I believe
                you<lb/> are acquainted! And other movements<lb/> made for the purpose of Organizing
                a<lb/> Congregation here, and for that purpose<lb/> the same gentleman was elected
                    <add>שוחת שוחט</add><lb/>
                <add>חזן מוהל</add>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I have been requested to order from you</p>
            <p>six copies of the large catechism for children</p>
            <p>“       “       small       “        “        “</p>
            <p>12       “        “       Primer       “        “</p>
            <p>Will you have the kindness to forward them<lb/> by Express to me with your bill for
                the same<lb/> which will be immediately paid.</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Very truly yours</p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">
                <persName role="author">J N Cardoza</persName>
            </p>
